{"id":634,"date":"2024-08-02T19:55:15","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T19:55:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=634"},"modified":"2024-08-02T19:55:15","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T19:55:15","slug":"tm037-sandstorm","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm037-sandstorm\/","title":{"rendered":"TM037 Sandstorm"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM037 Sandstorm<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Reward from the clown in the Great Desert after destroying all of the required smashable rocks.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>A 5-turn sandstorm that damages all Pok\u00e9mon types except Ground, Rock, and Steel.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Rock<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Dehara City<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm06-rock-smash\/\">Rock Smash<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Destroy every rock West and North-West of the Great Desert<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>From outside of the Dehara City Pok\u00e9mon Center, start by following the path North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-dehara-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Dehara City Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Dehara City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn East on the path behind the Dehara Game Center and continue going East.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-going-behind-the-game-center.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path going behind the Game Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path going behind the Game Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually enter the connector leading to the Great Desert.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-connector.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the connector. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the connector.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Inside the connector, continue heading East to exit instantly.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-walking-east-to-exit-the-connector.jpg\" alt=\"Walking East to exit the connector. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking East to exit the connector.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue on your path East even after entering the desert.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-walking-east-after-exiting-the-connector.jpg\" alt=\"Walking East after exiting the connector. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking East after exiting the connector.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start walking North when you hit the edge of a canyon.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-walking-north-when-the-path-east-gets-blocked.jpg\" alt=\"Walking North when the path East gets blocked. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking North when the path East gets blocked.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When the path to your right opens up, start going East again.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-continuing-east-when-possible.jpg\" alt=\"Continuing East when possible. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Continuing East when possible.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the second turn South and follow that path down.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-2nd-turn-south-and-following-the-path-down.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the second turn South and following the path down. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the second turn South and following the path down.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see a clown NPC trapped behind two smashable rocks here. <\/p>\n<p>Speak with him and he\u2019ll ask you to smash every breakable rock in the area\u2019s West and North-West side. Doing this will solve the clown puzzle and reward you with the TM for Sandstorm.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/09-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-npc-who-gives-sandstorm.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the NPC who gives Sandstorm. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the NPC who gives Sandstorm.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":635,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false}